name: Free Accounting Icons
description:
A pack of accounting and financial icons, carefully crafted to match your next accounting app or project, or even decorate your next money related presentation!


Some of the included icons are: bank, accounting, currency, money, calculator, bitcoin and more.


It includes Figma files as well as PNG and vector sources, so that you can adapt to your needs or resize without losing quality.


This freebie includes a personal usage license, but you can get our premium packs for using them without any restriction in any commercial project.


Highlights


  • Easy to edit and change colors
  • Organized components
  • Icons are scalable to any size you need
  • Easy to use for developers
  • Well organized icon names


Create your own icons with the icon mixer


Get a 2 million lifetime icon packs at a discounted price
